member.summary:
Adjust the width of the ScrollViewer when its content is resized.
If the vertical scroll bar is not visible, the with of the ScrollViewer should equal its content;
Otherwise, the scroll bar width should be accounted for.

This override is called whenever the view lines containing our adornments are edited or go out of view.
We use this override to keep our bind variable manager in sync with changes to the bind variable tokens;
specifically, to handle deletes and renames.

